data.description: All brick home with large level lot, fenced back yard with mature apple tree.  Fresh paint, New ceramic tile in kitchen/dinning and baths and New laminate wood gray flooring throughout, New light fixtures and fans, New kitchen counter tops, New doorknobs and 3 new interior doors. Outside has been power washed, caulked and painted.  Sellers are still painting inside and laying floors, but we feel like it is close enough at this point to show.   Available for showing on Oct 28, 2021
